snippet.title: 7 Wonders II (2007, PC) - 1 of 8: Stonehenge (England)[720p60]
snippet.description:
At least they introduced the free swapping rule starting with 7 Wonders II, I never work well with one-move-at-a-time system employed in various other Match-3s and in the first 7 Wonders

This gameplay was my first exposure to the 7 Wonders series, hence I was completely unaware of the proper system of building blocks and the "complete in 7 levels" format.

Map Puzzle solution — 10:23
